                    fontWeight: showGlow ? FontWeight.w600 : FontWeight.w400,
                  ),
                ),
              ),

              // State icon
              if (answered && isCorr)
                Container(
                  width: 28,
                  height: 28,
                  decoration: BoxDecoration(
